Rite Foods Limited, Nigeria’s manufacturer of carbonated soft drinks, energy drinks, and sausages, in its commitment to producing quality and refreshing products that appeal to consumers’ tastes, preferences and utmost satisfaction, has expanded its product portfolio with the launch of a new range of refreshing fruit drink, Sosa Fruit Drink. According to the management of the company, the new offering “is available in five flavours; Orange, Apple, Orange Passion and Mango, Mixed Berries, and Cranberry, with a refreshingly unique taste that is smooth. They are available for consumers in 35cl and 1-litre packs.” Mr. Seleem Adegunwa, Managing Director, Rite Foods Limited, while speaking on the launch, said the Truly World-class and Proudly Nigerian company’s fast strategy on innovation, prompted the introduction of the Sosa fruit drink to meet customers’ demands. Boluwatife Adedugbe, Brand Manager, Beverage and Bakery, Rite Foods Limited, in her remarks, buttressed that the Sosa Fruit Drink is an exceptional brand that guarantees the highest quality products for consumers’ refreshment.